NXP/Freescale Open-Source Sensor Fusion — magnetometer calibration
https://github.com/memsindustrygroup/Open-Source-Sensor-Fusion

License: BSD-3-Clause (Freescale Semiconductor, Inc.)

Only the magnetometer calibration (magnetic.c) and matrix math (matrix.c)
are included. Progressive 4/7/10 element calibration with accelerometer-based
spatial binning.

Local modifications:
- Added compat.h to replace NXP framework dependencies.
- Replaced custom int types with stdint.h.
- Removed NXP-specific includes.
